{"kanda":6,"sarga":18,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"अथरामःप्रसन्नात्माशृत्वावायुसुतस्यह ।प्रत्यभाषतदुर्धषश्रुतवानात्मनिस्थितम्","trans":"Having heard Hanuman (son of wind god) formidable Rama was highly pleased at heart and started to tell his opinion.","words":[{"d":"अथ:","m":"and then"},{"d":"दुर्धर्षः","m":"formidable one"},{"d":"श्रुतवान्","m":"one who heard"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"वायुसुतस्य:","m":"son of wind god's"},{"d":"शृत्वा:","m":"having heard"},{"d":"प्रसन्नात्मा:","m":"highly pleased at heart"},{"d":"आत्मनि:","m":"his own"},{"d":"स्थितम्","m":"that which was in his mind"},{"d":"प्रत्यभाषत:","m":"started to tell."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"ममापितुविवक्षाऽस्तिकाचित्प्रतिविभीषणम् ।श्रोतुमिच्छामितत्सर्वंभवद्भिश्श्रेयसिस्थितैः","trans":"\"Even I desire to speak a few words about Vibheeshana. I wish you, who are my well wishers and devoted to me, also hear me.\"","words":[{"d":"विभीषणंप्रति:","m":"about Vibheeshana"},{"d":"ममापि:","m":"even I"},{"d":"काचित्","m":"a few words"},{"d":"विवक्षा:","m":"desire to speak"},{"d":"आस्ति:","m":"is there"},{"d":"श्रेयसि:","m":"well wishers"},{"d":"स्थितैः","m":"are devoted"},{"d":"भवद्भिः","m":"you also"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"श्रोतुम्","m":"to hear"},{"d":"इच्छामि:","m":"I desire."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"मित्रभावेनसम्प्राप्तंनत्यजेयंकथञ्चन ।दोषोयद्यपितस्यस्यात्सतामेतदगर्हितम्","trans":"Although he (Vibheeshana) has defects, as he has come here with a friendly feeling, I cannot reject him. Good people are not reprehensible.","words":[{"d":"मित्रभावेन:","m":"with friendly feeling"},{"d":"सम्राप्तम्","m":"having come here"},{"d":"तस्य:","m":"his"},{"d":"दोष:","m":"defects"},{"d":"यद्यसि:","m":"although"},{"d":"कथञ्चन:","m":"however"},{"d":"नत्यजेयम्","m":"not reject"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"all this"},{"d":"सताम्","m":"good people"},{"d":"अगर्हितम्","m":"not reprehensible."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"सुग्रीस्त्वथतद्वाक्यमाभाष्यचविमृश्यच ।ततश्शुभतरंवाक्यमुवाचहरिपुङ्गवः","trans":"Then Sugriva, the leader of Vanaras reflecting on what was spoken by Rama said these words favouring Rama.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"then"},{"d":"हरिपुङ्गवः","m":"leader of Vanaras"},{"d":"सुग्रीवः","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"तद्वाक्यम्","m":"his statement"},{"d":"अभाष्यच","m":"and spoken by"},{"d":"विमृश्यच","m":"and reflecting upon"},{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"शुभतरम्","m":"favouring"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"उवाचह","m":"said."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"सुदुष्टोवाप्यदुष्टोवाकिमेषरजनीचरः ।ईदृशंव्यसनंप्राप्तंभ्रातरंयःपरित्यजेत् कोनामसभवेत्तस्ययमेषनपरित्यजेत् ।","trans":"\"Let this Rakshasa (night ranger) be a wicked one or not a wicked one, what have we to worry about such a person? He has come here abandoned by his brother and who will not send away such a person? Who will not do so?\"","words":[{"d":"एषः","m":"this"},{"d":"रजनीचरः","m":"night ranger"},{"d":"सुदुष्टोवा:","m":"be a wicked one"},{"d":"अदुष्टोवा:","m":"or not a wicked one"},{"d":"किम्","m":"what"},{"d":"यः","m":"with him"},{"d":"ईदृशम्","m":"such a person"},{"d":"व्यसनम्","m":"worry"},{"d":"प्राप्तम्","m":"has come here"},{"d":"भ्रातरम्","m":"when brother"},{"d":"परित्यजेत्","m":"had abandoned"},{"d":"तस्यएषः","m":"his this"},{"d":"यम्","m":"who"},{"d":"नपरित्यजेत्","m":"not abandon सः he"},{"d":"कोनाम:","m":"who will not"},{"d":"भवेत्","m":"do so."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"वानराधिपतेर्वाक्यंश्रुत्वासर्वानुदीक्ष्यच ईषदुत्स्मयमानस्तुलक्ष्मणंपुण्यलक्षणम् ।इतिहोवाचकाकुत्स्थोवाक्यंसत्यपराक्रमः","trans":"On hearing the words of the king of Vanaras, Rama of Kakuthsa dynasty and of truthful valour looked at all and threw a smile slightly at meritorious Lakshmana and spoke these words.","words":[{"d":"सत्यपराक्रमः","m":"one of truthful valour"},{"d":"काकुत्स्थ:","m":"of Kakuthsa dynasty"},{"d":"वानराधिपतेः","m":"of king of Vanaras"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा:","m":"on hearing"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"all"},{"d":"उदीक्ष्यतु:","m":"looking at"},{"d":"ईषत्","m":"slightly"},{"d":"उत्स्मयमानः","m":"throwing up a smile"},{"d":"पुण्यलक्षणम्","m":"meritorious characteristics"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"at Lakshmana"},{"d":"इति:","m":"these"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"उवाचह:","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"वानराधिपतेर्वाक्यंश्रुत्वासर्वानुदीक्ष्यच ईषदुत्स्मयमानस्तुलक्ष्मणंपुण्यलक्षणम् ।इतिहोवाचकाकुत्स्थोवाक्यंसत्यपराक्रमः","trans":"On hearing the words of the king of Vanaras, Rama of Kakuthsa dynasty and of truthful valour looked at all and threw a smile slightly at meritorious Lakshmana and spoke these words.","words":[{"d":"सत्यपराक्रमः","m":"one of truthful valour"},{"d":"काकुत्स्थ:","m":"of Kakuthsa dynasty"},{"d":"वानराधिपतेः","m":"of king of Vanaras"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा:","m":"on hearing"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"all"},{"d":"उदीक्ष्यतु:","m":"looking at"},{"d":"ईषत्","m":"slightly"},{"d":"उत्स्मयमानः","m":"throwing up a smile"},{"d":"पुण्यलक्षणम्","m":"meritorious characteristics"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"at Lakshmana"},{"d":"इति:","m":"these"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"उवाचह:","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"अनधीत्यचशास्त्राणिवृद्धाननुपसेव्यच ।नशक्यमीदृशंवक्तुंयदुवाचहरीश्वरः","trans":"\"That which has been spoken by the Lord of monkeys in this way is not possible for one who has not studied sastras or served the elders.\"","words":[{"d":"हरीश्वरः","m":"Lord of monkeys"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that which"},{"d":"उवाचह:","m":"has been said"},{"d":"ईदृशम्","m":"in this way"},{"d":"वक्तुम्","m":"to speak"},{"d":"शास्त्राणि:","m":"sastras"},{"d":"अनधीत्य:","m":"without studying"},{"d":"वृद्दान्","m":"elders"},{"d":"अनुपसेन्यच:","m":"to one who has served"},{"d":"नशक्यम्","m":"not possible."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"अस्तिसूक्ष्मतरंकिंचिद्यदत्रप्रतिभातिमे ।प्रत्यक्षंलौकिकंचापिविद्यतेसर्वराजसु","trans":"\"It strikes me that in this regard, as it is openly known for all the kings or at least in a subtle manner from a worldly point of view.\"","words":[{"d":"यत्","m":"that in this matter"},{"d":"सर्वराजसु:","m":"for all kings"},{"d":"प्रत्यक्षम्","m":"openly"},{"d":"विद्यते:","m":"known"},{"d":"लौकिकंचापि:","m":"even from worldly view"},{"d":"सूक्ष्मतरम्","m":"in subtle manner"},{"d":"किंचित्","m":"a little"},{"d":"अस्ति:","m":"is"},{"d":"अत्र:","m":"that"},{"d":"मे:","m":"to me"},{"d":"प्रतिभाति:","m":"strikes."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"अमित्रास्तत्कुलीनाश्चप्रातिदेश्याश्चकीर्तिताः ।व्यसनेषुप्रहर्तारस्तस्मादयमिहागतः","trans":"\"When in difficulty kings of the same clan of adjoining countries keep attacking the renowned and so they are declared as enemies. It is on account of this cause he (Vibheeshana) has come here.\"","words":[{"d":"तत्कुलीनाश्च:","m":"of kings of same clan"},{"d":"प्रातिदेश्याश्च:","m":"kings of adjoining countries"},{"d":"अमित्रा:","m":"not friendly ones"},{"d":"व्यसनेषु:","m":"when in difficulties"},{"d":"प्रहर्तारः","m":"keep attacking"},{"d":"कीर्तिताः","m":"renowned"},{"d":"तस्मात्","m":"on account of this"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"he has"},{"d":"इह:","m":"here"},{"d":"आगतः","m":"come."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"अपापास्तत्कुलीनाश्चमानयन्तिस्वकान्हितान् ।एषप्रायोनरेन्द्राणांशङ्कनीयस्तुशोभनः","trans":"\"The sinless ones respect the kings of their clan as friendly ones. But by and large such kings also do not believe the virtuous ones among the kings.\"","words":[{"d":"अपापाः","m":"sinless one"},{"d":"तत्कुलीनाः","m":"of the same clan"},{"d":"स्वकान्","m":"of their own"},{"d":"हितान्","m":"friendly ones"},{"d":"मानयन्ति:","m":"respect"},{"d":"प्रायः","m":"by and large"},{"d":"नरेन्द्राणाम्","m":"of the kings"},{"d":"शोभनः","m":"virtuous ones"},{"d":"एषः","m":"in this way"},{"d":"शङ्कनीयः","m":"do not believe."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"यस्तुदोषस्त्वयाप्रोक्तोह्यादानेऽरिबलस्यच ।तत्रतेकीर्तयिष्यामियथाशास्त्रमिदंशृणु","trans":"\"I will tell you what the scriptures have said about the demerit in accepting an enemy's strength that you have spoken. You may listen.\"","words":[{"d":"अरिबलस्य:","m":"regarding the enemy's strength"},{"d":"आदाने:","m":"accepting"},{"d":"यः","m":"that which"},{"d":"दोषः","m":"demerit"},{"d":"त्वया:","m":"by you"},{"d":"प्रोक्तः","m":"you have spoken"},{"d":"तत्र:","m":"there"},{"d":"ते:","m":"to you"},{"d":"यथाशास्त्रम्","m":"What the scriptures say"},{"d":"कीर्तयिष्यामि:","m":"will narrate to you"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"शृणु:","m":"you may listen."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"नवयंतत्कुलीनाश्चराज्यकाङ् क्षीचराक्षसः ।पण्डिताहिभविष्यन्तितस्माद्ग्राह्योविभीषणः","trans":"\"We do not belong to their clan. Among Rakshasas there are some learned ones. Vibheeshana has come because of his desire for their (Rakshasa) kingdom, perhaps ?\"","words":[{"d":"वयम्","m":"we"},{"d":"तत्कुलीनाःच:","m":"their clan"},{"d":"न:","m":"not"},{"d":"राक्षसः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"राज्यकाङ् क्षीच:","m":"and desire for their (Rakshasa) kingdom"},{"d":"पण्डिताः","m":"learned"},{"d":"भविष्यन्ति:","m":"desires"},{"d":"तस्मात्","m":"on account of this cause"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"ग्राह्यः","m":"can be accepted."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"अव्यग्राश्चप्रहृष्टाश्चनभविष्यन्तिसङ्गता ।प्रणादश्चमहानेषततोऽस्यभयमागतम् इतिभेदंगमिष्यन्तितस्माग्राह्योविभीषणः ।","trans":"\"Kinsmen will not be satisfied with one another and are not free from anxiety. That way they will not be together. Vibheeshana who has come out of fear in this way crying loudly for help and is worthy to accept.\"","words":[{"d":"अव्यग्राश्च:","m":"free from anxiety"},{"d":"प्रहृष्टाश्च:","m":"satisfied"},{"d":"सङ्गताः","m":"with one another"},{"d":"नभविष्यन्ति:","m":"will not be"},{"d":"इति:","m":"this"},{"d":"भेदम्","m":"difference"},{"d":"गमिष्यन्ति:","m":"will have"},{"d":"अतः","m":"and that way"},{"d":"अस्य:","m":"his (Vibheeshana's)"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"आगतम्","m":"has come"},{"d":"एषः","m":"this way"},{"d":"प्रणादश्च:","m":"crying for help"},{"d":"महान्","m":"loudly"},{"d":"तस्मात्","m":"as such"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"ग्राह्यः","m":"worthy to accept."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"नसर्वेभ्रातरस्तातभवन्तिभरतोपमाः ।मद्विथावापितुःपुत्रास्सुहृदोनाभवद्विथाः","trans":"\"O dear All brothers cannot be like Bharata, all sons will not be like me, or all friends like yo