 delusion"},{"d":"कामाद्वापि:","m":"even from desire"},{"d":"स्वया:","m":"his own"},{"d":"शक्त्वा:","m":"capacity"},{"d":"यथासत्त्वम्","m":"accordingly"},{"d":"नरक्षतिचेत्","m":"if he does not protect"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"लोकगर्हितम्","m":"censured by the world"},{"d":"पापम्","m":"sin."}]},{"v":29,"dev":"विनष्टःपश्यतस्तस्यारक्षिणश्शरणागतः ।आदायसुकृतंतस्यसर्वंगच्छेदरक्षित:।। 6.18.29।।","trans":"\"One who fails to protect a refugee who seeks protection from him is ruined in the eyes of the refugee and he takes away all the merit.\"","words":[{"d":"शरणागतः","m":"one who seeks protection"},{"d":"अरक्षितः","m":"fails to protect"},{"d":"तस्य:","m":"his"},{"d":"रक्षिणः","m":"refugee"},{"d":"पश्यतः","m":"in the eyes of"},{"d":"विनष्टः","m":"ruined"},{"d":"तस्य:","m":"his"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"all"},{"d":"सुकृतम्","m":"merit"},{"d":"आदाय:","m":"takes"},{"d":"गच्छेत्","m":"away."}]},{"v":30,"dev":"एवंदोषोमहानत्रप्रपन्नानामरक्षणे ।अस्वर्ग्यंचायशस्यंचबलवीर्यविनाशनम्","trans":"\"One who resorts to failure in protecting a refugee, will be doing a great sin that way and will be shut out of heaven, be infamy and his strength and virility will be lost.\"","words":[{"d":"प्रपन्नानाम्","m":"resorts to"},{"d":"अत्रअरक्षणे:","m":"that way fails to protect"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"महान्","m":"great"},{"d":"दोषः","m":"sin"},{"d":"अस्वर्ग्यम्","m":"out of heaven"},{"d":"अयशस्यंच:","m":"and infamy"},{"d":"बलवीर्यविनाशनम्","m":"strength and virility gets lost."}]},{"v":31,"dev":"करिष्यामियथार्थंतुकण्डोर्वचनमुत्तमम् ।धर्मिष्ठंचयशस्यंचस्वर्ग्यंस्यात्तुफलोदये","trans":"\"Excellent and meaningful words have been said by sage Kandu (about one who protects a refugee), that is by doing one's righteous duty. He will be not only famous but reach heaven as a result of his action.\"","words":[{"d":"कण्डोः","m":"of Kandu"},{"d":"उत्तमम्","m":"excellent"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"यथार्थम्","m":"meaningful"},{"d":"करिष्यामि:","m":"has said"},{"d":"धर्मिष्ठम्","m":"one who doe