 king of birds. ।। इत्यार्षेवाल्मीकीयेश्रीमद्रामायणेआदिकाव्येयुद्धकाण्डेअष्टादशस्सर्गः ।। This is the end of the eighteenth sarga of Yuddha Kanda of the first epic the holy Ramayana composed by sage Valmiki.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"नरेश्वरः","m":"king"},{"d":"तत्","m":"there"},{"d":"सुग्रीववचः","m":"Sugriva's words"},{"d":"निशम्य:","m":"perceiving"},{"d":"पुरन्दरः:","m":"like Indra"},{"d":"पतत्त्रिराजेनयथा","m":"like with the king of birds"},{"d":"विभीषणेन:","m":"with Vibheeshana"},{"d":"अशु:","m":"as said"},{"d":"हरीश्वरेण:","m":"by Sugriva"},{"d":"अभिहितम्","m":"very fitting"},{"d":"सङ्गमम्","m":"meeting"},{"d":"जगाम:","m":"went."}]}]}